# mlisp procmail recipes
# Generated sample — copy or append to ~/.procmailrc
#
# Replace /usr/local/bin/mlisp and /home/user/.config/mlisp with your paths.
# To install automatically:
#   mlisp-admin install-procmail [--list <id>] [--dry-run]

# mlisp: discuss
:0
* ^TO_denzuko+mlist-discuss@panix.com
| /usr/local/bin/mlisp --home /home/user/.config/mlisp discuss

# mlisp: announce
:0
* ^TO_denzuko+mlist-announce@panix.com
| /usr/local/bin/mlisp --home /home/user/.config/mlisp announce

# mlisp: devel
:0
* ^TO_denzuko+mlist-devel@panix.com
| /usr/local/bin/mlisp --home /home/user/.config/mlisp devel
